file: bmptk/core/README

Bare Metal Programming Tool Kit core functionality directory

This directory contains :

   files
      - basics.h           : basic declarations (time, types)
      - bmptk.cpp          : implementations of some basic functions
      - channels.h         : data channels
      - context.cpp        : context (stack) switching
      - context.h
	   - Makefile           : dummy makefile
      - memory.cpp         : memory allocation
      - memory.h
      - README             : this file
      - rtos.cpp           : simple RTOS
      - rtos.h
      - time.h             : time ADT

